# Frontmatter
- Always include frontmatter in the following format so that the site is published correctly:
```yaml
---
layout: default
title: Page Title Here
---
```

## Frontmatter exceptions
- README.md: No frontmatter needed

## Title guidance
<title> is a placeholder.  Use the page’s main # heading or a short human-readable page name

# Formatting
- Use simple hyphens for lists.  E.g.:
```markdown
- Item 1
- Item 2
```

- Never leave a blank line between a heading and the first line of content
